### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">وَيَـٰقَوْمِ أَوْفُوا۟ ٱلْمِكْيَالَ وَٱلْمِيزَانَ بِٱلْقِسْطِ ۖ وَلَا تَبْخَسُوا۟ ٱلنَّاسَ أَشْيَآءَهُمْ وَلَا تَعْثَوْا۟ فِى ٱلْأَرْضِ مُفْسِدِينَ</span>

### English

O  my people! Give full measure and weigh with justice. Do not defraud people of their property, nor go about spreading corruption in the land.